msgid ""
"KDE Menu Edit lets you edit how your apps are presented in application "
"launchers, such as Plasma's Application Launcher widget."
msgstr ""
"KDE valmyndaritill gerir þér kleift að breyta því hvernig forritin birtast í "
"forritaræsum eins og forritaræsi Plasma."
